Yiwu Fair 2024
Event Information
Since 1995, Yiwu Fair has been a reliable platform for businessmen to expand their market shares both domestically and abroad. As the third largest export-oriented commodities fair in China, Yiwu Fair is authorized by the State Council and is jointly hosted by the Ministry of Commerce, the People's Government of Zhejiang Province and other relevant authorities.
The Yiwu Fair is held annually at the intersection of Zongze Rd & East Jiangdong Rd, Yiwu, China. It is renowned for its internationalization and informativeness, as well as the excellent services and security it provides. Every year, the event attracts numerous exhibitors and visitors, making it one of the largest and most productive commodities fairs in China.
The Yiwu Fair is a great opportunity for businesses to explore the Chinese market and gain a competitive edge. With its slogan of "face to the world, serve the whole nation", the Yiwu Fair is an ideal platform for exhibitors to showcase their products and services, build connections, and gain valuable insights into the Chinese market.

Company Profile
Yiwu Bichang Import & Export Co., Ltd. was established in 2015. The company is located in Yiwu City, Zhejiang Province, which is known as "the capital of small commodities in the world". At present, our company operates 3C digital accessories export business. Helping clients with their commodities purchasing management and products design, which is our business philosophy all the time.
Our Customers
Customers that we have served from Europe's leading
supermalls and supermarkets, overseas small and medium-sized wholesalers, retailers. In the past seven years, we has maintained good cooperative relationship with overseas clients in many countries around the world. Our company supply a range of value-added services including commodities purchasing, product researching, package designing, product testing, quality control, International logistics coordination and so on for customers.
